featured_reviews.review_id:
In olden days there were 3 sanatorium, Haideri,Rupawala and Bootwala. It was pleasent and calm. Over the years it has changed a lot. The new name is Saify park etc.
The road has become busier and noisy. Now there are no rooms to stay. It has turned to marrige hall and religious sermons.
There is facilities for handicapped persons, parking is not available. Toilets are good.
This place is restricted to Dawoodi Bohras only.
